image.altText: A composite image showing Donald Trump looking the right and Kamala Harris looking to the left.

props.synopsis: Millions of Americans are beginning to head to the polls to decide whether Kamala Harris or Donald Trump should win the race to the White House. Follow live.

image.altText: An extremely thin girl wearing a black leotard in a dancer's pose in front of a blue wall, face blurred.
